title: Prime Witness
subTitle: Jayaraman, a visually impaired lift operator, is blamed for a murder. Jayaraman must try to find the real murderer and prove his innocence.

subTitle: A distraught woman decides to exact revenge on the ruthless gangsters who framed her husband during a police encounter, making her lose him and her unborn baby.

subTitle: A young college boy who is disappointed with his family's middle-class lifestyle decides to escape it by joining a popular college and having a wealthy girlfriend.

title: Jersey
subTitle: A former cricketer in his late 30s returns to the sport to fulfil his son's dream of owning a cricket jersey, battling personal and professional challenges.

title: Vijay The Master

title: RRR
subTitle: A fearless revolutionary and an officer in the British force, who once shared a deep bond, decide to join forces and chart out an inspirational path of freedom against the despotic rulers.

title: Radhe
subTitle: Radhe, a daredevil encounter specialist of the Mumbai Police force, vows to knock down the crime syndicate led by an evil drug lord.

title: Kaliveera
subTitle: Evil forces with differing interests plot to steal a Shiva linga for profit. However, a young tribal man rises up to protect it by any means necessary.

title: Dabangg 2

title: Dabangg 2

title: Ka Pae Ranasingam
subTitle: Ariyanachi, a poor woman, strives to bring her deceased husband's body back to India from Dubai, battling the odds of political agenda, corruption and a treacherous bureaucracy that stand in her way.

title: Dhartiputra
subTitle: Yashpal tries to rape Jeeva and her husband, Shiva, stops him while she manages to escape. However, Yashpal kills him and she vows to avenge his death.

title: Sooryavanshi

title: Bhimaa
